{"tid":659423,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"正負評係俾個post值唔值得多啲人睇，唔係俾佢嘅內容","createTime":"2018-05-09T20:21:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-10T17:28:52.000Z","uid":60238,"like":6,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"091685bd7324a9be2ad728c613bbd98dcd3693c1","tid":659423,"uid":60238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T20:21:02.000Z","msg":"唔知開邊，開返時事台<br />\n<br />\n呢樣嘢想講好耐<br />\n舉個例先<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/659248/1?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/659248/1?ref=android</a><br />\n新移民夫婦兩度誕下唐氏綜合症子女向醫管局要求賠償<br />\n<br />\n好似呢個post咁，明明佢只係一篇仆街新移民嘅新聞，但有二百幾個負評<br />\n我覺得咁樣有問題，負評應該係俾嗰啲開鳩post既人，唔係你唔鐘意個新聞內容就俾，何況係呢類轉貼嘅post<br />\n雖然呢單新聞令人好燥底(廢老娶大陸婆，大陸婆攞身份證，生個弱智嘥政府錢)，但都應該俾返正評，等多啲人入嚟睇啲咁荒謬但又影響緊我地嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n鳩up完畢，多謝各位"},{"pid":"820ebd52c4affdd0641551729c4a1b98e1c3c1b5","tid":659423,"uid":19214,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T20:41:47.000Z","msg":"同意啊"},{"pid":"65aae392e275547ef6672a4a659020abd2120bef","tid":659423,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T21:46:31.000Z","msg":"唔通見負皮就唔撚入咩 你都戇撚柒鳩鳩"},{"pid":"53d334a93540d2413114d9991da29158ff436a1e","tid":659423,"uid":31323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65aae392e275547ef6672a4a659020abd2120bef","tid":659423,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T21:46:31.000Z","msg":"唔通見負皮就唔撚入咩 你都戇撚柒鳩鳩"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T21:59:37.000Z","msg":"j圖post見到大量負皮你入唔入？"},{"pid":"56704b97bd2d9d3a8d1a211dd130b47386010842","tid":659423,"uid":65400,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"53d334a93540d2413114d9991da29158ff436a1e","tid":659423,"uid":31323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65aae392e275547ef6672a4a659020abd2120bef","tid":659423,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T21:46:31.000Z","msg":"唔通見負皮就唔撚入咩 你都戇撚柒鳩鳩"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T21:59:37.000Z","msg":"j圖post見到大量